msgid "Customer"
msgstr "Pelanggan"

msgid "Manual Adjustment"
msgstr "Penyesuaian Manual"

msgid "Promotion"
msgstr "Promosi"

msgid "Order Refund"
msgstr "Pengembalian Pesanan"

msgid "Order Payment"
msgstr "Pembayaran Pesanan"

msgid "Get wallet balance"
msgstr "Dapatkan Saldo Dompet"

msgid ""
"Get the authenticated customer's wallet balance. Creates a wallet "
"automatically if the customer does not have one."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan saldo dompet pelanggan yang terautentikasi. Membuat dompet secara "
"otomatis jika pelanggan tidak memiliki satu."

msgid "Authentication required"
msgstr "Autentikasi Diperlukan"

msgid "List wallet transactions"
msgstr "Daftar Transaksi Dompet"

msgid ""
"Get the authenticated customer's wallet transaction history, ordered by most"
" recent first. Supports filtering by type, source, and status."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan riwayat transaksi dompet pelanggan yang terautentikasi, diurutkan "
"berdasarkan yang terbaru terlebih dahulu. Mendukung penyaringan berdasarkan "
"jenis, sumber, dan status."

msgid "Filter by transaction type"
msgstr "Saring Berdasarkan Jenis Transaksi"

msgid "Filter by source"
msgstr "Saring Berdasarkan Sumber"

msgid "Filter by status"
msgstr "Saring Berdasarkan Status"

msgid "Number of results (default 20, max 100)"
msgstr "Jumlah hasil (default 20, maks 100)"

msgid "Pagination offset"
msgstr "Offset Paginasi"

msgid "List customer wallets"
msgstr "Daftar Dompet Pelanggan"

msgid ""
"List all customer wallets. Supports search by email or name, and filtering "
"by active status."
msgstr ""
"Daftar semua dompet pelanggan. Mendukung pencarian berdasarkan email atau "
"nama, dan penyaringan berdasarkan status aktif."

msgid "Search by customer email or name"
msgstr "Cari berdasarkan email atau nama pelanggan"

msgid "Filter by active status"
msgstr "Saring Berdasarkan Status Aktif"

msgid "Get wallet details"
msgstr "Dapatkan Detail Dompet"

msgid "Get full details of a customer wallet."
msgstr "Dapatkan detail lengkap dari dompet pelanggan."

msgid "Credit a wallet"
msgstr "Kreditkan Dompet"

msgid ""
"Manually add credit to a customer's wallet. Requires amount, currency, "
"source, and description."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan kredit secara manual ke dompet pelanggan. Membutuhkan jumlah, mata"
" uang, sumber, dan deskripsi."

msgid "Invalid input or wallet frozen"
msgstr "Input tidak valid atau dompet dibekukan"

msgid "Debit a wallet"
msgstr "Debitkan Dompet"

msgid ""
"Manually debit a customer's wallet. Fails if the wallet has insufficient "
"balance or is frozen."
msgstr ""
"Kurangi kredit secara manual dari dompet pelanggan. Gagal jika dompet "
"memiliki saldo yang tidak cukup atau dibekukan."

msgid "Insufficient balance, invalid input, or wallet frozen"
msgstr "Saldo tidak cukup, input tidak valid, atau dompet dibekukan"

msgid "Toggle wallet freeze"
msgstr "Ubah Status Bekukan Dompet"

msgid ""
"Freeze or unfreeze a customer's wallet. A frozen wallet cannot process "
"credits or debits."
msgstr ""
"Bekukan atau thawar dompet pelanggan. Dompet yang dibekukan tidak dapat "
"memproses kredit atau debet."

msgid "Wallet is frozen"
msgstr "Dompet Dibekukan"

msgid "Wallet credited successfully"
msgstr "Dompet Berhasil Dikreditkan"

msgid "Insufficient wallet balance"
msgstr "Saldo dompet tidak cukup"

msgid "Wallet debited successfully"
msgstr "Dompet berhasil didebit"

msgid "unfrozen"
msgstr "tidak beku"

msgid "frozen"
msgstr "beku"

#, python-format
msgid "Wallet %s successfully"
msgstr "Dompet %s berhasil"

msgid "List all transactions"
msgstr "Daftar semua transaksi"

msgid ""
"List wallet transactions across all customers. Supports filtering by wallet,"
" type, source, status, and search."
msgstr ""
"Daftar transaksi dompet di seluruh pelanggan. Mendukung penyaringan "
"berdasarkan dompet, jenis, sumber, status, dan pencarian."

msgid "Filter by wallet ID"
msgstr "Saring berdasarkan ID dompet"

msgid "Search by customer email"
msgstr "Cari berdasarkan email pelanggan"

msgid "Number of results (default 50, max 100)"
msgstr "Jumlah hasil (default 50, maks 100)"

msgid "Get transaction details"
msgstr "Dapatkan detail transaksi"

msgid "Get full details of a wallet transaction."
msgstr "Dapatkan detail lengkap dari transaksi dompet."

msgid "Available Balance"
msgstr "Saldo Tersedia"

msgid "Current spendable balance"
msgstr "Saldo yang dapat digunakan saat ini"

msgid "Pending Balance"
msgstr "Saldo Tertunda"

msgid "Credits not yet available (e.g. pending refund window)"
msgstr ""
"Kredit belum tersedia (misalnya, jendela pengembalian dana yang tertunda)"

msgid "Lifetime Credited"
msgstr "Kredit Seumur Hidup"

msgid "Lifetime Used"
msgstr "Digunakan Seumur Hidup"

msgid "Active"
msgstr "Aktif"

msgid "Deactivate to freeze this wallet"
msgstr "Nonaktifkan untuk membekukan dompet ini"

msgid "Last Credited At"
msgstr "Terakhir Dikreditkan Pada"

msgid "Last Used At"
msgstr "Terakhir Digunakan Pada"

msgid "Customer Wallet"
msgstr "Dompet Pelanggan"

msgid "Customer Wallets"
msgstr "Dompet Pelanggan"

